<section anchor="code-snippets"><name>Code snippets</name>

<t anchor="_d57ffeca-d03e-0f85-152f-e74a84c56f1f">Code snippets should be wrapped with <tt>&#x3c;CODE BEGINS&#x3e;</tt> and
<tt>&#x3c;CODE ENDS&#x3e;</tt> blocks, as required by the IETF Trust Legal
Provisions (TLP) <xref target="IETF.TLP">4 parens</xref> specified in <xref target="RFC5378"></xref>.</t>
</section>
</section>
